# Manual Builds Only

Do not compile, build, or run the project yourself. The user builds manually.

## Do not run

- `xcodebuild`
- `swift build`
- Opening/running the app in Simulator via CLI
- Any other build, compile, or run step meant to verify changes

## Instead

- Make the code changes
- Briefly note what the user should run if verification is needed (e.g. **⌘R** in Xcode)
- Only run builds if the user explicitly asks you to
